Battery & Charging Module → Main Board (XH-S3E-AI_V1.0)
● Battery Positive (+) → Charging Module B+
● Battery Positive (+) → Switch → VIN
● Battery Negative (-) → Charging Module B-
● Battery Negative (-) → GND

OLED Display → Main Board
● GND (Black Wire) → GND
● VDD (Red Wire) → 3V3
● SCK (Blue Wire) → IO42/SCL
● SDA (Green Wire) → IO41/SDA

Speaker → Main Board
● Speaker Cable (Red & Black Wires) → White Connector Port (Bottom Right)
